{
  "chapter": 17,
  "chapter_summary": "第十七回\"残暴之尤\"以楚留香推理柳无眉真实身份为起点。楚留香指出柳无眉是石观音派往江南的卧底，李玉函虽知真相却仍维护妻子，几近癫狂。柳无眉在众人逼问下终于坦白身世：她与曲无容均为石观音收养的孤儿，石观音对她们表面亲近实则残忍——不仅杀了曲无容的父母，更在柳无眉出谷时在酒中下毒，迫使其依赖罂粟维生。柳无眉揭露了此前暗杀楚留香未遂的真相：她假称生病，以丫头代为呻吟掩饰行踪，用暴雨梨花钉偷袭。她坦承因石观音之毒日益发作、罂粟难以为继，才铤而走险刺杀楚留香——因为据她所知，世上只有一人能克制石观音，而此人正是楚留香。本章以柳无眉提到这位\"最可怕的人\"作结，留下悬念。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因为那些人也想不到她会下这毒手，所以才对她全没有防备，否则以一人之力，又怎能在片刻中杀死那么多人……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "如此说来，你认为就因为她是石观音最亲近的人，所以她才想要杀你，是么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除此之外，似乎再也没有别的解释。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那么我呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你只怕也上了她的当，被她利用了……也许她根本就是石观音派到江南来卧底的奸细，所以才嫁给你，用‘拥翠山庄’少庄主夫人的名义来作掩护，自然是再好也没有的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她既是石观音的死党，为何却去解了胡铁花他们中的毒?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因那时我已杀了石观音，她见到大势已去，所以才去救了他们，也好为日后留个退步，反正胡铁花他们若是死了，对她也没什么好处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "楚留香呀楚留香，你实在太聪明了，只可惜聪明得过了度。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我难道说错了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你自然没有说错，无所不知的楚留香怎会错呢?现在无论你怎么说，反正已全都没什么关系了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只因你现在反正已非死不可，否则我就立刻杀了她们。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你疯了么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错，我的确疯了，但你若换了我，你只怕比我疯得更厉害。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到现在为止，你还要庇护她?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到现在为止，你难道还不相信她是石观音那女魔头的门下?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错，我本是石观音门下，但我从来也没有瞒着他。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_li_yu_han",
      "text": "你早已知道她是石观音派到江南来卧底的奸细，还要娶她作老婆，除了她之外，天下的女人难道都死光了不成?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么恶毒的话都被你们说尽了，能不能也让我说几句话?",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "在下正在洗耳恭听。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "石观音所收的弟子，只有我和曲无容是从小就跟着她长大的，我们两人都是孤儿，甚至连自己父母的名姓都不知道，她本来替我取了个名字，我到这里后，才指柳为姓，易名无眉。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "曲无容的名字，莫非也是容貌被毁之后才更改的么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，她本来叫无思，我本来叫无忆。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无思、无忆、无花……唉!",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她虽然想要我们无思无忆，怎奈我们却也是有血有肉的人，每个人长大了都会思念自己的父母，我们自然也不例外，怎奈她却始终不肯说出我们的父母是谁，我们只要一提这件事，她就会发脾气。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她对她门下子弟的手段，我是亲眼瞧见过的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她只有对我和曲无容两人特别好些，不过曲无容的性情比较孤僻刚强，又不会说讨她欢喜的话，我却比较……",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你却比较会拍人的马屁，这我倒知道的，你若想讨人欢喜时所说的话，听得入耳朵都要流出油来。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在别人眼中看来，石观音好像真的是石头雕成的，但她也是个有血有肉的人，她也有人的弱点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有时候，她也会觉得忧愁烦恼，寂寞痛苦，到了这种时候，她也会借酒浇愁，而且常会喝得大醉。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到石观音还有这么样一件好处。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因为她对我比较亲近，所以常常要我陪她一起喝酒，有一天她又喝醉了，竟对我说出一件秘密。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "什么秘密?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那天喝到天快亮的时候，她已醉得眼睛发直，忽然告诉我，曲无容的父母就是被她杀死的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "她难道就为了要收曲无容做徒弟，所以杀死她的父母?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我听了她的话，又是吃惊，又是害怕，当时我就想到，曲无容的父母既是被她杀死的，那么我的父母呢?",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你为什么不趁她喝醉时问问她?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我自然问过她，她却说，我的身世和曲无容不同，我是别人的弃婴，连她都不知道我的父母是谁，我再问她，她就搂着我痛哭起来，说她自己连一个亲人都没有，始终将我当做她亲生的女儿一般看待。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "她一哭，你就相信了么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽然不信，却也找不出什么证据，更不敢将这秘密告诉曲无容，因为我若告诉了她，反而等于害了她。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，石观音若知道曲无容已发现这秘密，她是绝不会再留她活在世上的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从那天晚上之后，我表面上看来虽然还是和以前一样，其实我的心里已经变化，再也不能像以前那么样和她亲近了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "曲无容的变化却比我更大，她年纪越长，对石观音就越疏远，她就好像是一朵在空谷中的幽兰，看来总是那么冷漠，那么高贵，那么忧郁，那么美，我虽然是个女人，但连我都觉得她实在是真美，美得令人不敢去沾染她，更不敢去攀折她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜我们竟无缘一睹她那时的颜色。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜天妒红颜，我……我实在也未想到石观音竟会毁去她的容貌……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你也知道那是石观音下的毒手?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道这件事后，更觉得无法和石观音相处了，她虽然再三告诉我，叫我放心，说她绝不会向我下毒手的，可是在我眼中，她已变成了一条毒蛇，她只要瞧我一眼，我都无法忍受。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你难道是逃出来的么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有逃，我若想逃，也就活不到现在了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只是说：‘我已是大人了，已经应该出来见见世面。’我从小就生长在那荒漠的穷谷中，连外面的世界是什么样子都不知道，所以我求她放我出来。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "她怎么说?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她什么都没有说，只问我，什么时候要走?",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你怎么说?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那时我只觉连一天都呆不下去了，我就说：‘最好是明天’。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "她难道居然答应了么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她听了我的话，沉默了很久，忽然说：‘好，我今天晚上替你饯行。’我也想不到她居然会答应，真是开心极了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你开心得只怕还太早了些。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当天晚上，她果然准备了酒莱为我饯行，我……我究竟是她养大的，想到明天就要和她分别，心里也不免有些伤感，想到她竟如此爽快的让我走，又不免对她很感激，所以那天晚上，我又陪她喝了一夜。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "第二天呢?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第二天早上，她就送我出谷，放我走了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她就这样放你走了么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她就这样放我走了，因为她算准我一定会回去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还未走出五百里，就觉得腹痛如绞，就好像有条极小的毒蛇在我的肠子里蠕动着，用毒牙在咬着我的心肝。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "酒……酒中有毒?",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，酒中有毒，所以她算准我一定会爬着回去求她，否则我就要死在沙漠里，连收尸的人都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她既已答应放你走，为什么又要在酒中下毒?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为她要我知道她的厉害，要我永远不敢背叛她，要我跪在地上求她……她喜欢看别人哀求她的样子。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好这人现在已经死了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她虽然阴险毒辣，却还是忘记了一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她忘了自己喝醉酒的时候，曾经告诉我许多秘密。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她难道将解毒的秘密也告诉了你?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是她的门下，自然也学会不少下毒解毒的本事，否则阁下只怕也活不到现在了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "但她对你下的毒，却必定是她未曾教给你解法的，你甚至根本就不知道她下的是什么毒，又如何去解?",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这道理我自然明白，可是她却告诉过我，罂粟虽能使人沉沦，但有时却也是止痛解毒的良药，因为它能使人完全麻醉，根本忘记了痛苦，所以我早就偷偷藏了一匣自罂粟提炼出的白色粉末，因为我随时都在提防着她下毒手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一旦一个人若是终日在麻醉中，又与死何异?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我自然也知道若以罂粟来止痛，实在无异饮鸩止渴，但是那时我实在已痛得无法忍受，而且我宁死也不愿再回去求她，永远做她的奴隶。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "于是你就做了罂粟的奴隶。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "这些年来，你的日子一定很不好过。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "如此说来，那天半夜你在那客栈中呻吟呼号，也是因为病毒发作，并不是假装的了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，以前我毒发时只要一服罂粟，痛苦立止，但最近这些日子，就算用比以前多两倍的罂粟来止痛，也不如以前那么有效。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这并不是因为罂粟已失去止痛之力，而是因为你整个人都已渐渐被它麻木，就正如上了酒瘾的人，酒必定越喝越多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一点也不错，以前我喝酒时，只要喝上个三五杯，就会觉得飘飘欲仙，忘却了所有烦恼，但现在我就算喝上三五斤烧刀子，还是好像没喝一样。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "那天你既然是真的有病，用暴雨梨花钉来暗算我们的人又是谁呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也是我。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "我明明听到你在屋里穷叫，又怎能出来暗算人呢?你……你总不至于会分身术吧?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "罂粟止痛虽已不如从前有效，但也用不着那么多时候，我听得你们已走出院子，就要一个丫头装出我的呻吟声，每个人痛苦时声音都会变样子的，所以你们就算觉得声音有异，也不会怀疑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你将暴雨梨花钉抛在树林里，自然也是为了怕被我们发现了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们根本没有去找那七根指头的老前辈，因为世界上根本就没有那么样一个人，是么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非但没有他这个人，就连‘熊老伯’也是杜撰的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们故意说要去找人，就因为你们已花了二十万两银子买了个凶手，他行刺的时候，你们一定不能在场，否则你们就不必找他来了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁知他却被楚留香捉住了，你们怕泄漏机密，就只有将他杀了灭口。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一点也不错。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我现在才知道你真是个活诸葛，简直料事如神。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这些事，你难道早已猜到了么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "但我实在猜不出你为何要杀我?你既非为石观音报仇，却又是为了什么呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是为了我自己。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "你自己?你自己难道和我有什么仇恨?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我和你并没有仇恨，但是你不死，我就得死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "近年来，我毒发的次数越来越密，需要的罂粟也越来越多，我带出来的那一匣早已用完了，要到江湖上去搜购，更不知有多么困难，我也知道像这样子下去，我纵不死于石观音之毒，也要死于罂粟之毒。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "确是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我自己受苦倒没什么，但……但我实在不忍拖累了他，他为了我这病，为了去找罂粟，已不知花了多少钱，受了多少苦。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这件事你不必说的。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事已至此，我一定要将所有的事全都说出来……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你早就该说出来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "据我所知，石观音平生只怕一个人，她曾说过，这人简直是她的克星，她所有的本事，若用到这人面前，就变得不值一文。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦!世上还有这么样一个人么?是谁?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我就想，这人只怕能解得了石观音的毒。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你发觉自己中毒的时候，就该去找这人了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽然早已想去找他，可是又一直不敢。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怕什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因他不但是世上武功最高的人，也是世上最可怕的人，他的性格根本无法捉摸，脾气更是喜怒无常，既不明是非，也不辨善恶，只要他高兴，他什么事都做得出，杀死个把人，在他说来简直比捏死只蚂蚁还容易。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样的人，我倒想和他斗斗。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    }
  ],
